C IF ENERGY GT X1S2(N1S2) EV USE BEF SCALING
  401 QIN(4,I)=0.1590/(EIN(4)*BETA2)*(DLOG(BETA2*GAMMA2*EMASS2/(4.0*
     /EIN(4)))-BETA2-DEN(I)/2.0)*BBCONST*EN/(EN+EIN(4)+E(3))  
