C 5S1!    BEF SCALING
 1270 IF(EN.LE.EIN(43)) GO TO 2000
      QIN(43,I)=0.00250/(EIN(43)*BETA2)*(DLOG(BETA2*GAMMA2*EMASS2/(4.0*
