C ---------------------------------------------------------------------      
C    NEW ANALYSIS UPDATED TO NOVEMBER 1999.
C    ALLOWS SUPERELASTIC SCATTERING TO ALL VIBRATIONAL LEVELS
c    EXCLUDING VIBRATION HARMONICS.
C    BORN ANGULAR DISTRIBUTION FOR  V1(0.1001) AND V2(0.1523) LEVELS.
C --------------------------------------------------------------------       
